*openvpn-2.1.3 (27 Sep 2010)

  27 Sep 2010; Dirkjan Ochtman <djc@gentoo.org> +openvpn-2.1.3.ebuild:
  Version bump to 2.1.3.

  27 Sep 2010; Dirkjan Ochtman <djc@gentoo.org> -openvpn-2.0.9.ebuild,
